title: Elmira Corning Regional airport receives an update in MSFS
description:
The Elmira Corning Regional Airport (KELM) has recently been updated in MSFS, enhancing its realism for flight simulation enthusiasts. If you enjoy flying in the New York area and prefer a smaller airport, KELM could be an excellent choice to consider.
